{"tid":37933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"12月12日鬼幣又創新低","createTime":"2016-12-13T15:17:37.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T08:57:34.000Z","uid":46804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"871d15309d66f4e8016a82e4de882573b9f31256","tid":37933,"uid":46804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:17:37.000Z","msg":"12日，人民幣兌美元中間價報6.9086，再度跌破6.9，下調114點，創11月25日來最低。<br />\n<br />\n據路透社12日消息，有外匯交易員表示，強勢美元仍是人民幣下跌的主要外因，大陸銀行依然在市場上提供美元流動性，預計人民幣短期仍存較大下行壓力。而離岸人民幣貶值預期仍較重，離岸即期與在岸價差午後擴大至逾250點。且離岸人民幣資金利率早盤時段趨緊，導致離岸拆借利率各期限紛紛走高，不過午後隨著流動性緊張有所緩解，拆借利率有所回落。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，一年期離岸掉期和在岸同期掉期價差逾2,200點，創近11個月來最大，也凸顯離岸資金看空人民幣預期。"},{"pid":"28b84c51a1a79be42d5cab4f23b51f78652c0af4","tid":37933,"uid":46804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:17:56.000Z","msg":"準備香賓"},{"pid":"e52861ebfbad4cf300cea64bce93b521950b915f","tid":37933,"uid":6745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:18:38.000Z","msg":"熱烈地"},{"pid":"1cc0091c27cfcf03ab873f4e82c139b834ab7005","tid":37933,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:19:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf9b9bcdc1e66ae2d993d76e12d4adb12250e33","tid":37933,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T18:34:20.000Z","msg":"1兌1先講啦"},{"pid":"a0bdd4e2a843c3fffe36869c7b3369c156b32c33","tid":37933,"uid":153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T18:39:50.000Z","msg":"根本就要好似以前咁0.9鬼幣兌1港紙咁先叫正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d119ee32285412496dcf9c70ed29d060d3a8da","tid":37933,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T18:45:26.000Z","msg":"買買買"},{"pid":"a7dedef446d1d9165a0af790d81d020d4cfcad2b","tid":37933,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T22:16:25.000Z","msg":"之前印左咁多，你估唔駛還？<img src=\"/a